Screen Open 0,320,256,4,LORES
Flash Off : Curs Off : Hide : Cls 0
Double Buffer : Autoback 0

X0=Rnd(310)+5
Y0=Rnd(250)+5
X1=Rnd(310)+5
Y1=Rnd(250)+5
X2=Rnd(310)+5
Y2=Rnd(250)+5
X3=Rnd(310)+5
Y3=Rnd(250)+5
AX=2
AY=3
BX=1
BY=2
CX=4
CY=2
DX=1
DY=2

Ink 2
While Mouse Key<>2
If X0>=319 or X0<=1 Then AX=-AX
X0=X0+AX
If Y0>=255 or Y0<=1 Then AY=-AY
Y0=Y0+AY
If X1>=319 or X1<=1 Then BX=-BX
X1=X1+BX
If Y1>=255 or Y1<=1 Then BY=-BY
Y1=Y1+BY
If X2>=319 or X2<=1 Then CX=-CX
X2=X2+CX
If Y2>=255 or Y2<=1 Then CY=-CY
Y2=Y2+CY

If X3>=319 or X3<=1 Then DX=-DX
X3=X3+DX
If Y3>=355 or Y3<=1 Then DY=-DY
Y3=Y3+DY

Wb Spline X0,Y0 To X1,Y1 To X2,Y2,12
Wb Spline X0,Y0 To X3,Y3 To X2,Y2,12

Screen Swap
Cls 0
Wend
